    "name": "Twitter: Obvious Advertisements",
    "description": "I don't mind seeing Twitter ads, but they tend to look very similar to normal content.\r\nThis style fixes that by giving them a different (configurable) background colour.",
    "additionalInfo": "2017-08-14: The style now also affects promoted accounts (without hover effect to match Twitter's default behaviour).\r\n2017-08-14: Fixed bug causing descendants of promoted tweets to be coloured in too.\r\n2017-10-13: The style now also affects promoted trends.",
